Function ChgStr(str,table,key)
    For i=1 To Len(str)
        one=Mid(str,i,1)
        flag=FALSE
        For j=1 To Len(table)
			If one=Mid(table,j,1) Then ChgStr=ChgStr&Mid(key,j,1):flag=TRUE:Exit For
        Next
        If flag=FALSE Then ChgStr=ChgStr&one 
    Next
End Function
